{"slideshow_credits": null, "snippet": "Innovation may outpace the supply of the rare metals that power it.", "abstract": "Op-Ed article by author David S Abraham warns increased reliance on alternative energy sources in effort to fight global warming will result in increased dependence on rare metals used to make green technology; notes process of extracting speciality metals, including rare earths, is slow as well as politically and environmentally fraught, sparking fears that technological demand will outpace supply; urges government intervention aimed at extracting rare metals faster and more inexpensively with minimal environmental impact.", "section_name": "Opinion", "print_page": "31", "document_type": "article", "byline": {"person": [{"lastname": "ABRAHAM", "rank": 1, "firstname": "David", "role": "reported", "organization": "", "middlename": "S."}], "original": "By DAVID S. ABRAHAM"}, "web_url": "http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/20/opinion/the-next-resource-shortage.html", "lead_paragraph": "Innovation may outpace the supply of the rare metals that power it.", "headline": {"print_headline": "The Next Resource Shortage?", "main": "The Next Resource Shortage?", "content_kicker": "Op-Ed Contributor", "kicker": "Op-Ed Contributor"}, "_id": "564ed7f538f0d84d3be11227", "word_count": "852", "multimedia": [{"height": 126, "url": "images/2015/11/20/opinion/20abrahamWeb/20abrahamWeb-thumbWide.jpg", "legacy": {"wideheight": "126", "wide": "images/2015/11/20/opinion/20abrahamWeb/20abrahamWeb-thumbWide.jpg", "widewidth": "190"}, "subtype": "wide", "width": 190, "type": "image"}, {"height": 402, "url": "images/2015/11/20/opinion/20abrahamWeb/20abrahamWeb-articleLarge.jpg", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2015/11/20/opinion/20abrahamWeb/20abrahamWeb-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": "600", "xlargeheight": "402"}, "subtype": "xlarge", "width": 600, "type": "image"}, {"height": 75, "url": "images/2015/11/20/opinion/20abrahamWeb/20abrahamWeb-thumbStandard.jpg", "legacy": {"thumbn